Author: scarletssstarktitan
Content: sorry ,i am not sure about understanding  your question ,Starknet is a permissionless Validity-Rollup (also known as a “ZK-Rollup”) that supports general computation and currently operates in production as an L2 network **over Ethereum.** and official bridge starkgate is the message（token) bridge which only support starknet and L1 ethereum , not rely on other L2 chain to verify the message , here is details https://docs.starknet.io/documentation/architecture_and_concepts/Network_Architecture/token-bridge/ thank you
